    "title": "京东开放平台发布违禁商品及信息管理规范-药品实施细则",
    "followRuleId": "1206154529616302080",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">京东开放平台发布违禁商品及信息管理规范中对应章节标准：</span></span></strong></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.9</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">药品、医疗器械类：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.9.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">国家实行特殊管理的药品</span> </span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">背景：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">请遵守《中华人民共和国药品管理法》、《药品网络销售监督管理办法》、《兴奋剂目录》、《互联网药品信息服务管理办法》等相关法律法规的规定。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规则定义：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">麻醉药品、精神药品、医疗用毒性药品、放射性药品、易制毒药品、蛋白同化制剂、肽类激素（胰岛素除外）、终止妊娠药品、戒毒药品、医疗机构制剂、血液制品、疫苗、兴奋剂、注射剂(降糖类药物除外） 、含麻黄碱类复方制剂（不包括含麻黄的中成药）、含麻醉药品口服复方制剂、含曲马多口服复方制剂、右美沙芬口服单方制剂等，如可卡因、（伪）麻黄碱、人血白蛋白、艾司唑仑、米非司酮等。</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.nmpa.gov.cn/yaopin/ypggtg/20221130200847133.html\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">国家药监局关于发布药品网络销售禁止清单</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">标准：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">平台禁止发布上述药品，请勿使用上述药品名进行商品宣传（蹭词）</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">案例：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"wscnph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://img30.360buyimg.com/venderrule//jfs/t1/280375/4/21425/22251/6806fdbdF0fcffab0/06e9245d9e2cf333.png\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: white;\">温馨提示：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">如您发布的商品被误拦截，请联系客服通知相关人员进行系统优化</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.9.2<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">我国法律法规规定的零售企业不得经营的药品</span> </span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: white;\">规则定义：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">国家毒性药品管理品种中规定的毒性中药品种和西药毒性品种等，如生川乌、阿托品等。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: white;\">标准：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">平台禁止发布上述药品，请勿使用上述药品名进行商品宣传（蹭词）</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: white;\">案例：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"><img class=\"wscnph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://img30.360buyimg.com/venderrule//jfs/t1/282824/14/22602/30040/6806fde4F50fe51e8/8f5dbcb8a13a3296.png\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: white;\">温馨提示：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">如您发布的商品被误拦截，请联系客服通知相关人员进行系统优化</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.9.3<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">根据国家法律法规或京东治理要求，京东认定可能存在高风险的禁售药品（含跨境药品等）</span> </span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: white;\">背景：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">请遵守《中华人民共和国药品管理法》、《互联网药品信息服务管理办法》、《放射性药品管理办法》、《麻醉药品和精神药品管理条例》、《医疗用毒性药品管理办法》、《血液制品管理条例》等相关法律法规的规定。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: white;\">规则定义：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">高风险药品，如高风险部位或高风险用法的注射剂、晕车药等，如静脉注射、静脉滴注、动脉注射、关节腔内注射、玻璃体内注射、浸润麻醉等用法的注射剂；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">②</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">跨境药品包括但不限于：国内明确禁止上架药品、高风险药品：治疗窗窄药品（抗凝血药、镇痛药、肿瘤药）、抗精神疾病药品、癫痫药（存在自杀倾向ADR风险）、性激素类药品、毒性成份药品、与疫情防控相关的处方药品等；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">③</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京